videos.description: Texas State wide receiver L.G. Williams takes the quick pass and throws the ball back to quarterback Tyler Jones in the open field, which gives Texas State the 56-48 lead over Ohio after the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Triple overtime, double pass, one TD
